codex
I have enough context to write the verifier. The implementation will stay path-strict: it will only attempt unauthorized `transferFrom(victim, attacker, amount)` calls with `amount > minted`, targeting concrete existing-balance victims exposed by on-chain public state, and it will fall back to a no-profit state if burn-side preconditions make the path infeasible.
